text: Input/Output Data The Input/Output data is the type of data an agent expects and delivers. The agent expects ConnectionRequestUDR s and RequestUDR s. The agent returns ConnectionStateUDR s, ResponseUDR s and ErrorUDR s. MIM The agent does not publish nor access any MIM parameters.
title: TCP/IP Processing Agent Input/Output Data and MIM - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
